name: Psychedelic Skull Drip
description: A mind-melting fusion of chaos and style, this NFT showcases a surreal, melting skull with exposed brains, draped in neon colors that radiate a trippy, psychedelic aura. Sporting sleek shades with bold insignias and a punk-inspired jacket adorned with custom patches, this character oozes rebellion and attitude. A mischievous, snake-like tongue stretches out, embodying pure energy and unfiltered expression. This is a symbol of the wild, the fearless, and the unapologetically unique.
